|               |   Sort: u DESC NULLS FIRST                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                   |
|               |     Projection: hits.MobilePhoneModel, count(DISTINCT hits.UserID) AS u                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      |
